# TV Playlist Editor

Manage FrogoTV channel playlists — list, add, remove, reorder videos.

Use when the user says "kill that video", "remove video", "add video to playlist", "reorder playlist", "list playlist", "what's playing", or references editing a channel's videos.

## Arguments

- `$ARGUMENTS` — the action and details (e.g., "remove Dolphins from kids-animals", "list philosophy", "add VIDEO_ID to business at position 3")

